h1. error

h2. Purpose

Shows an error-type [Window.Notification|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Window.Notification.html] in the application's main window.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
<v:error>Hello world!</v:error>
{code}

h2. Description 

h4. Body

* Used as the notification message - can be raw HTML.

h4. Attributes

{note}
See Vaadin [Window.Notification|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Window.Notification.html] API docs for full list of allowed attributes
{note}